subject: Hockey, Ice
lead_paragraph: Dany Heatley, Jason Spezza and Mike Fisher scored to lead the host Ottawa Senators to a 3-2 victory over the Rangers on Saturday night in the first preseason game for both teams. Brandon Dubinsky scored the Rangers’ goals.
